```plantuml
@startuml jzyong_GameServer4g

actor Client
participant Gate
participant Hall
participant World
participant Resource
participant "ZooKeeper" as ZK
participant "API (Login/Charge)" as API

== Deployment Phase ==
Gate -> ZK : Register service (gate)
Hall -> ZK : Register service (hall)
World -> ZK : Register service (world)
Resource -> ZK : Register service (res)
API -> ZK : Register service (api)

== Runtime Connectivity ==

Client -> Gate : TCP connection (custom protocol)
Gate -> ZK : Discover available halls
ZK --> Gate : Hall service list
Gate -> Hall : gRPC connection (selected hall)

Hall -> ZK : Discover available worlds
ZK --> Hall : World service list
Hall -> World : gRPC connection (selected world)

Client -> Gate : Game message (protobuf)
Gate -> Hall : Forward message (gRPC)
Hall -> World : Process game logic (gRPC)
World --> Hall : Response (gRPC)
Hall --> Gate : Response (gRPC)
Gate --> Client : Response (TCP)

== Additional Interactions ==
Client -> API : Login/Charge requests
API -> Resource : Access game resources
Resource --> API : Return resources
API --> Client : Response

@enduml
```